column2: SELECT     s.bestobjid, d7.specObjID, d7.dr7ObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, p.mjd, s.mjd, f.mjd_u, f.mjd_g, f.mjd_r, f.mjd_i, f.mjd_z, s.class, p.type, g.sigma_balmer, g.sigma_forbidden, s.veldisp, e.bpt into mydb.MyTable_# from PhotoObjAll AS p     JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid     JOIN Field AS f ON f.fieldid = p.fieldid     JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid     JOIN SpecDR7 AS d7 ON d7.specObjID = s.specObjID     JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.specobjID = s.specObjID WHERE     s.z BETWEEN # AND #     AND p.type = #     AND s.class = &&&     AND g.sigma_balmer BETWEEN # AND #
